- If the instance inventory in the region is greater than this value, instances are created based on other configured parameters.', example='20'),
  ownerAccount?: string(name='OwnerAccount'),
  ownerId?: long(name='OwnerId'),
  payAsYouGoAllocationStrategy?: string(name='PayAsYouGoAllocationStrategy', description='The strategy for creating pay-as-you-go instances. Valid values:

