Default value: None.

When both a launch template and launch configuration parameters are specified, the launch template takes precedence.', example='Standard'),
    dataDisk?: [ 
      {
        autoSnapshotPolicyId?: string(name='AutoSnapshotPolicyId', description='The automatic snapshot policy ID applied to the data disk.

