- This parameter takes effect only when creating an auto provisioning group with AutoProvisioningGroupType=instant.', example='sp-bp67acfmxazb4p****'),
        burstingEnabled?: boolean(name='BurstingEnabled', description='Specifies whether to enable performance burst. Valid values:

