> This parameter is supported only when DiskCategory is set to cloud_auto. For more information, see [ESSD AutoPL](https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/368372.html).', example='40000'),
        size?: int32(name='Size', description='The size of data disk N, in GiB. N ranges from 1 to 16. Valid values:

